'''天主教巴爾的摩總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Baltimorensis}}；{{lang-en|Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Baltimore}}）是[[美國|美國]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]和美國第一個天主教教區（總主教為美國[[首席主教|首席主教]]），也是該國32個總教區之一。

總教區下轄[[天主教惠靈-查爾斯頓教區|惠靈]]、[[天主教阿靈頓教區|阿靈頓]]、[[天主教威爾明頓教區|威爾明頓]]和[[天主教里士滿教區|里士滿]]四個教區，範圍包括[[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]]中西部。總教區有48萬6607名教友，面積為4800[[平方英里|平方英里]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Our History |url=https://www.archbalt.org/the-archdiocese/our-history/ |publisher=Archdiocese of Baltimore |accessdate=2020-01-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125085535/https://www.archbalt.org/the-archdiocese/our-history/ |archivedate=2020-01-25 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。現任總主教為[[威廉·愛德華·羅利|威廉·愛德華·羅利]]<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 20.03.2012 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/03/20/0166/00382.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-01-25 |language=it |date=2012-03-20 |archivedate=2020-01-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125092511/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/03/20/0166/00382.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-en|亞當·帕爾克|Adam Parker|亞當·若望·帕爾克}}和{{link-en|布魯斯·萊萬多夫斯基|Bruce Lewandowski}}<ref name="Vatican20161205">{{cite press release |title=Other Pontifical Acts, 05.12.2016 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2016/12/05/161205b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-01-25 |language=en |date=2016-12-05 |archivedate=2020-01-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125092604/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2016/12/05/161205b.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 10.06.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/10/200610b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-06-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610125434/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/10/200610b.html |archivedate=2020-06-10 |language=en |date=2020-06-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休輔理主教為{{link-en|特尼斯·J·馬德登恩|Denis J. Madden}}<ref name="Vatican20161205" />。

教區於1789年11月6日成立，1808年4月8日升為總教區；1939年易名為'''巴爾的摩-華盛頓總教區'''。[[天主教華盛頓總教區|華盛頓總教區]]於1947年成立，恢復原名。

